# Analytics Configuration
# =====================

# Google Analytics 4 - Get your ID from https://analytics.google.com
# Format: G-XXXXXXXXXX
NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX

# Meta Pixel (Facebook Pixel) - Get from https://business.facebook.com/events_manager
# Format: 15-16 digit number
NEXT_PUBLIC_META_PIXEL_ID=000000000000000

# Hotjar (Optional) - Get from https://www.hotjar.com
# Format: 7 digit number
NEXT_PUBLIC_HOTJAR_ID=0000000

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env.local
# 2. Replace the placeholder values with your actual IDs
# 3. Restart the dev server after making changes
# 4. Never commit .env.local to version control
